Name: JQ: cosmos
About the game: JQ: cosmos - this is a quiz game about space. In this game you are expected by questions on 3 subjects: planets, astronauts and constellations, and also 2 mini-games with endless gameplay: 'What planet is bigger?'and 'Which planet is closer to the sun?'. Choose the correct answer among the 4 options offered to pass the next level. Features: 50+ levels 3 main themes and 2 mini-games with endless gameplay Interesting soundtrack Steam Achievements Credits: This game was created using Clickteam Fusion 2.5! Music by Erwarda Savitnaag.
